      <title>美国银行布兰奇：大宗商品价格因需求不足而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-30/commodities-falling-due-to-lack-of-demand-bofa-s-blanch-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美银证券大宗商品和衍生品研究主管弗朗西斯科·布兰奇（Francisco Blanch）研究了委内瑞拉政治动荡、需求不足导致油价下跌对石油的潜在影响，以及金价上涨背后的因素。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-30/commodities-falling-due-to-lack-of-demand-bofa-s-blanch-video</guid>
